title.narrative: Support to improved Security & Justice activity in high and medium priority countries, as per National Security Council priorities.

description.narrative: This activity (Support to improved Security & Justice activity in high and medium priority countries, as per National Security Council priorities.) is a component of Establishing a centre of excellence for Security and Justice activity related to fragile and conflict affected states. reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £742,591. This component benefits Developing countries, unspecified, and works in the following sector(s): Research/scientific institutions. , with the following implementing partners: Crown Agents Limited. The start date is 01-04-2013 and the end date is 31-03-2015.
